dct_title_s: Plano de la ciudad de Buenos Aires
dct_description_sm: Verso: map of Buenos Aires showing three classes of roads, railroads. Includes public transportation index, and railroad distances from Buenos Aires to other cities. Oriented with north towards the right.
dct_publisher_sm: Buenos Aires, Argentina : Departamento de Cartografía Peseur, 1965.
